summary:
Computer Science Engineer highly motivated for investigation, development, and support, with excellent interpersonal skills applied to multicultural environments.
With more than ten years of experience, my expertise includes both hands-on troubleshooting skills, and theoretical knowledge in Unix, Linux, Mac OS X, and Windows operating systems, having as well knowledge IT infrastructure like Cisco networking, NetApp and Quantum storage solutions, VMware vSphere/Fusion virtualization platforms.
